      "text": "World Model\n\nEnvironmentStateService\n+ AttackGraphService\n\n— hosts\n— subnets\n— credentials\n— compromised agents\n— reachability graph\n\nrebuilt every step\nserialized into the prompt\n\n(this is why the LLM\nhas memory)",
